title: Dining Out With Timon And Pumbaa - Norsk Tale
description:
<a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/Timon-And-Pumbaa-Dining-Volume/dp/B0006M4S5U" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.amazon.co.uk/Timon-And-Pumbaa-Dining-Volume/dp/B0006M4S5U</a>

'Dining Out With Timon and Pumbaa' (1997) was one of three videos released containing six episodes of the hilarious 'The Lion King' TV spinoff 'Timon and Pumbaa'. I loved it as a kid and I love it now. It was great to see that it is now out on DVD.

The compilation contains the following six episodes:

French Fried
Russia Hour
Swiss Missed
To Kilimanjaro Bird
Don't Break the China
Rocky Mountain Lie
as well as the music video 'Yummy, Yummy, Yummy'.

The show is far more comic than the films (which of course are far superior) and are great fun. This is a great choice of episodes and each one is very entertaining.
